    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been really well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that still looks great on the road! It runs like a champ and is ready for many more miles of adventures. I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too. Come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
