      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Cayman S is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine architecture provides an ideal polar moment of inertia, complemented by a well-sorted suspension featuring MacPherson struts and stiffened anti-roll bars. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the engine exhibits strong compression and linear power delivery across the tachometer. Braking performance is anchored by four-piston monoblock aluminum calipers over vented rotors. This example retains the communicative hydraulic steering rack, offering tactile feedback that newer EPS units lack. A mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
