    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm selling my reliable ride and it's honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so while it has a little bit of character from the road, it runs beautifully and is ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and well-maintained because I wanted it to stay dependable. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a great car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it drives! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
