      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, supported by a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension geometry. While displaying minor cosmetic patina typical of a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical integrity is excellent, with the double-VANOS system and rod bearings recently serviced to ensure peak performance and longevity.",
